# Analytics Events Specification

This document defines the events and metrics tracked in the todo application for Hackathon II.

## Core Events

### User Lifecycle Events
- `user_signed_up`
- `user_logged_in`
- `user_logged_out`
- `user_profile_updated`

### Task Management Events
- `task_created`
- `task_completed`
- `task_deleted`
- `task_edited`
- `task_priority_changed`
- `task_assigned`

### ChatKit Events
- `chat_message_sent`
- `chat_message_received`
- `tool_call_initiated`
- `tool_call_success`
- `tool_call_failure`
- `chat_session_started`
- `chat_session_ended`

### Feature Usage Events
- `feature_discovered`
- `feature_used`
- `feature_shared`
- `feature_feedback_submitted`

## Event Properties

### Common Properties
- `user_id` (string): Unique user identifier
- `timestamp` (datetime): When the event occurred
- `session_id` (string): User session identifier
- `platform` (string): Web, mobile, desktop
- `version` (string): App version
- `source` (string): Where the event originated

### Task-Specific Properties
- `task_id` (string): Unique task identifier
- `task_priority` (string): Priority level (low, medium, high, urgent)
- `task_category` (string): Category of task
- `time_spent` (number): Time spent on task in seconds
- `completion_method` (string): How task was completed

### Chat-Specific Properties
- `message_id` (string): Unique message identifier
- `message_length` (number): Length of message in characters
- `tool_name` (string): Name of tool called
- `tool_success` (boolean): Whether tool call succeeded
- `chat_duration` (number): Duration of chat session in seconds

## Key Metrics

### User Engagement
- Daily Active Users (DAU)
- Monthly Active Users (MAU)
- DAU/MAU ratio
- Session duration
- Feature adoption rate

### Task Performance
- Tasks created per user per day
- Tasks completed per user per day
- Task completion rate
- Average time to complete tasks
- Task abandonment rate

### ChatKit Performance
- Messages per user per day
- Tool call success rate
- Chat session duration
- Response time
- Error rate

## Privacy & Compliance
- All events are GDPR compliant
- User data is anonymized where possible
- Users can opt-out of analytics
- Data retention policy: 2 years
